397
00:15:21.935 --> 00:15:23.775
Porque el señor de Penáguilas,

398
00:15:24.095 --> 00:15:25.775
que era un sí,

399
00:15:26.095 --> 00:15:26.735
es no,

400
00:15:27.260 --> 00:15:28.940
